### Available Commands

| Command | Action | Learning Loop Stage |
|---------|--------|---------------------|
| `resume` | Pull + load last handoff | — |
| `remember <slug>` | Save memory entry | 1. CAPTURE |
| `recall <keyword>` | Search memory | 2. APPLY (pre) |
| `apply <memory>` | Bump applied_count + announce | 2. APPLY |
| `audit` | Session health report | 4. EVOLVE |
| `promote <memory>` | Graduate to AGENT.md | 5. PROMOTE |
| `evolve <slug>` | Graduate a repeated workflow into an executable skill | 6. EVOLVE SKILL |
| `supersede <old> <new>` | Mark an old memory superseded by a new one | — |
| `archive <slug>` | Archive a stale memory entry | — |
| `save` | Save session context only (no audit/commit/push) | — |
| `handoff` | Audit + save + commit + push | 4. EVOLVE |

